Personal repository for interesting advice I've heard following the *If you do X 3 times, then do Y* pattern.

> If you copy and paste code 3+ times, write a function
> 
> If you copy and paste a function 3+ times, write a package
>
> `r tufte::quote_footer("--- Hadley Wickham")`

> If you give in-persone advice 3+ times, write a blog post
>
> `r tufte::quote_footer("--- [David Robinson](https://twitter.com/drob/status/928447584712253440)")` 

